    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1165990/extras/4a48d145be005a0385e618e33cd84d0e.avif?t=1769107867\" alt=\"Kiln\" width=780 height=198 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1165990/extras/c086474394397b69a0dbdc3bd8d08cad.avif?t=1769107867\" alt=\"烈火淬炼，陶艺争霸\" width=780 height=112 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1165990/extras/b88f19ac3d9879fbcc52a6cc552f62e0.avif?t=1769107867\" alt=\"\"width=780 height=480 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1165990/extras/59f38a698d1151f2c2d774b87240da3b.avif?t=1769107867\" alt=\"Double Fine Productions倾情呈献，一场献给玩家的在线陶艺派对格斗盛宴。\" width=780 height=176 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1165990/extras/2bab8ab60d35b565f8f6898ad4bd3f4b.avif?t=1769107867\" alt=\"\"width=780 height=448 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1165990/extras/4ef14a35ac5d8fbff1ea17f0308d2fd9.avif?t=1769107867\" alt=\"呼朋唤友，集结各色神灵，转动陶轮，亲手捏塑陶瓷战甲。\" width=780 height=176 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1165990/extras/a29fd90ec660427c4ca37c7aa7bc317e.avif?t=1769107867\" alt=\"\"width=780 height=448 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1165990/extras/405e220e9bc16358d000d6133465361b.avif?t=1769107867\" alt=\"陶器身躯的尺寸与形状决定了你的战斗风格与技能——齐心协力，浇灭敌人的窑火！\" width=780 height=176 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Kiln》是一场关于陶艺的狂想曲，它既歌颂创造，也拥抱毁灭：你不仅能体验精雕细琢之美，更能享受将其粉碎成渣的极致快感。捏个陶罐，叫上好友，化身五彩神灵加入在线竞技场的对决。你在陶轮上精心打造的瓷器，就是随你征战沙场的肉身。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >陶器的形状决定了你的属性与风格。是要大块头还是小个子？是宽厚敦实还是高挑细长？你想化身为盘、为壶、为杯，还是为碗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >海量尺寸组合等你探索，每种搭配都赋予你独特的技能与攻击方式，带来意想不到的新奇玩法。协同作战，摸索出陶器与战术的最佳搭配，撕开敌方防线。收集水源，浇灭敌人窑炉的烈火——你的团队能否兼具塑造之才与粉碎之力，从而杀出一条通往胜利的血路？当战场上遍布敌我双方破碎的陶瓷残片，唯有精湛的格斗技巧与默契的团队配合，方能锁定胜局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >胜仗归来，不妨去“揉泥工坊”磨炼陶艺技法，装饰陶器彰显个性，并与他人分享你的杰作（顺便瞻仰一下别人的手艺）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >同塑共碎——捏陶也好，碎陶也罢，与朋友一起总是更开心。闲庭信步，玩转泥土，分享创意；或者直接投身多人乱斗，大打出手！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >晋升陶艺大师——在沉浸式的陶轮体验中，利用各式工具与技法操控拟真泥土，尽情创作与装饰。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
